===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|underwriten}}, from {{inh|en|ang|underwrītan|t=to write at the foot of, write under, subscribe}}, equivalent to {{prefix|en|under|write}}. Compare {{cog|nl|onderschrijven|t=to endorse}}, {{cog|de|unterschreiben|t=to sign; endorse}}.

